(- Runtime Deletion and Recovery Expectations) Tj
T*
(- Deleting a consensus store while the node is running is unsafe.) Tj
T*
(- Store open paths attempt recovery or reopen when practical.) Tj
T*
(- Missing or corrupt required state should fail closed rather than letting the node continue on) Tj
T*
(uncertain state.) Tj
T*
(- Operationally, stop the node before manual LMDB deletion unless you are intentionally testing) Tj
T*
(recovery behavior.) Tj
T*
(- Map Growth and Rollover) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Atho uses bounded LMDB map growth:) Tj
T*
(- on MapFullError, stores may grow map size when enabled,) Tj
T*
(- growth is capped by store limits,) Tj
T*
(- near-limit pressure is logged.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Important:) Tj
T*
(- LMDB page reuse does not shrink map size automatically,) Tj
T*
(- pruning or cleanup frees pages for reuse but does not compact file size.) Tj
